{"tid":1131722,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"遊走於DC及Marvel的男人David Dastmalchian加盟《自殺特攻2》飾演Polka-Dot Man","createTime":"2019-04-30T00:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T09:03:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed36d6764fefb044191ecdb38f89efa7005f79a3","tid":1131722,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:06:42.000Z","msg":"Ant-Man actor David Dastmalchian is headed over to the DC universe.<br />\n<br />\nDastmalchian has closed a deal to star in James Gunn's The Suicide Squad, with sources saying he will play the comic book villain Polka-Dot Man.<br />\n<br />\nThe actor now joins Margot Robbie, who is returning as villain turned sometime heroine Harley Quinn; Jai Courtney, back as Captain Boomerang; and Idris Elba, who was initially set to take on the role of Deadshot before a script change saw it evolve into a new, undisclosed part.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-sequel-casts-david-dastmalchian-as-polka-dot-man-1205280?utm_source=Sailthru&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=THR%20Breaking%20News_2019-04-29%2011:21:00_acouch&amp;utm_term=hollywoodreporter_breakingnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fheat-vision%2Fsuicide-squad-sequel-casts-david-dastmalchian-as-polka-dot-man-1205280%3Futm_source%3DSailthru%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_campaign%3DTHR%2520Breaking%2520News_2019-04-29%252011%3A21%3A00_acouch%26utm_term%3Dhollywoodreporter_breakingnews&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=d1672b8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-sequel-casts-david-dastmalchian-as-polka-dot-man-1205280?utm_source=Sailthru&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=THR%20Breaking%20News_2019-04-29%2011:21:00_acouch&amp;utm_term=hollywoodreporter_breakingnews</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nweOsDk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr