2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呢個都係"},{"pid":"110173aefba7e494e1cce52cd5853a7162942865","tid":1131722,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a009158a9e79f2a8c05f39e55535b57f3ede021","tid":1131722,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2f37d9120b5db53424af3370491a2fbdf02dc078","tid":1131722,"uid":3405,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orgs.pub/images/image/25/2571489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orgs.pub%2Fimages%2Fimage%2F25%2F2571489.jpg&h=59139ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢都係喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/g2qh59dcbwl21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fg2qh59dcbwl21.png&h=65c708b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呢個都係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:47:30.000Z","msg":"who.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb0a134b45fec933de17f61e2a93ca67b9c5e88","tid":1131722,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"詹姆士&middot;岡恩執導和編劇的ＤＣ漫畫改編電影《自殺突擊隊》（The Suicide Squad），今天再度確定一名演員將飾演自殺突擊隊的新成員，那就是在漫威蟻人兩部電影都有演出的 David Dastmalchian。<br />\n<br />\n他飾演的角色為 Polka-Dot Man（波爾卡圓點人），初次登場在 1962 年發行的偵探漫畫第 300 期，衣服的圓點可以用來放置各種武器和進行傳送，但雖然能力上很方便這角色智商太低所以很容易被擊倒。<br />\n<br />\n目前除了四位新角色，還有未知的角色要給另一位ＭＣＵ跳槽過來的演員伊卓瑞斯&middot;艾巴（Idris Elba）飾演；除此之外在舊角色方面，上一集的三位演員－薇拉&middot;戴維絲（Viola Davis）、瑪格&middot;蘿比（Margot Robbie）和傑&middot;寇特尼（Jai Courtney）等都會回歸，藉此證明此部電影只是政策重啟而非世界觀上的重啟。<br />\n<br />\n《自殺突擊隊》預計在 2021 年 8 月 6 日推出。"}]}